  "about_title": "📄 About Us",
  "about_story_title": "📖 TechYar Story",
  "about_story_text": "TechYar was born about 3 years ago!<br>The initial idea came from a PowerPoint presentation with the same stick figure on the first page, which I created for the course \"Radiographic Techniques\"!<br><br>My idea was welcomed by our university professor <a href=\"https://cv.hums.ac.ir/cv/2ef132b1-f801-45f3-8158-afbcf083a05e\" class=\"about-link-person\" data-person=\"dr-afzali\">\"Dr.Reza Afzalipoor\"</a>, and with the help of the only programmer I knew at the time, <a href=\"https://github.com/chahar4\" class=\"about-link-person\" data-person=\"agha-reza\">\"Reza Charsetad\"</a>, we decided to turn it into an Android app!<br>It was a good idea, it worked, the beta version was ready but never reached release...<br><br>After that, I decided to start coding myself, and now that idea, after years of gathering dust, has returned stronger and become a web app, so it can run on all platforms (Android, iOS, etc.) 😌",
  "about_developer_title": "👨‍💻 Developer",
  "about_developer_name": "Mohammad Hossein Mahdipanah",
